  "instructions": [
    "In a sous-vide cooker, prepare anchovy fillets in a water bath at 60°C for 45 minutes.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat, add garlic and oregano, sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add diced tomatoes, lemon zest, and red wine (if using), cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Layer the sous-vide anchovies over the tomato mixture, sprinkle with parsley, and cover.",
